metadata.name: All That Jazz
metadata.description:
Seattle, Washington. 
Pike Place Market
Nikon FM2 and Rollei RPX 100
Observing the man's cheerful demeanor and playful interactions with passersby, I savored his lively performance before capturing this snapshot. His music and dance left a lasting impression, setting a joyful tone for the rest of the day. This brief encounter was a delightful and memorable experience.
Enjoy my postcard from the Emerald City.
